  ChaiN2-iuN7 kong2 chong-kau3 kau3-iok8 si7 ¡§to7-siong7¡¨ kau3-iok8 hoat te7-it ho2? Chhi3-siuN7 li2 kiam2 e7 eng7-tit eng7 to5-ia2 e5 hong-sek, lai5 nge7 chhih8 hak8-seng hou7 i chiaN5-choe3 chit8 e5 sim2-mih8 bou5-heng5 e5 sin3-giong2-tek e5 jin5-but8, tek8-piat8 tui3 ti7 ¡§sin3-giong2 si7 chu7-iu5--e5.¡¨ Siong7-te3 tou chun-tiong7 lang5 e5 chu7-iu5 soan2-tek8 e5 i3-chi3, hong7-kiam3 lau7-su, li2 u7 sim2-mih8 leng5-lek8, thang tui3 ti7 sin3-giong2 lai5 kiong5-che3 to5-ia2 nih? A2-si7, li2 kiam2 e7-tit tui3 ji5-tong5 e5 lai7-bin7 eng7 khe2-hoat, thiu chhut sim2-mih8 ho2 lai5 chou7-tiong5 hou7 i khah seng5 Chu2, soa3 e7 tit-tioh8 kiu3. Seng3-chheh lai7 kiam2 m7 si7 kong2 lian5 poaN3 e5 ho2 lang5 to bo5? Li2 beh tui3 hak8-seng, pi7 kau3-iok8-chia2 e5 lai7-bin7 thiu chhut sim2-mih8 ho2, lai5 khe2-hoat--i ah? Bo5 lah. 
