  TaN lan2 i2-keng chai beh hou7 gin2-na2 tit-tioh8 sin3-giong2, hou7 in e7 chiap-siu7 Ia5-sou, tui3 Ia5-sou Ki-tok hou7 se3-kiaN2 u7 koan5 thang hok8-kui chiaN5 choe3 Siong7-te3 e5 kiaN2-ji5, che long2 m7 si7 tui3 lau7-su e5 to5-ia2, koan3-chu3, khe2-hoat, a2-si7 thiu-chhut e5 sou2 e7 thang cho7-chiaN5 e5. Chi2 u7 chiu7-si7 po3 se3-kiaN2 khoaN3 Ia5-sou, chhoa7 se3-kiaN2 lai5 chiu7-kun7 Chu2, hou7 Chu2 chhin-sin ka7 in hoaN7-chhiu2 chiok-hok in ,lan2 chi2 u7 chiu7-si7 chhoa7 in chiuN7 kau3 ti7 Chu2 e5 bin7-cheng5. 
