  Lang5 siong5-siong5 ai3 kong2 ¡§Lin2 tioh8 chu3-sin5 khoaN3 Ia5-sou, m7-thang khoaN3 goa2¡¨, che si7 to5 chek-jim7 e5 oe7. Ia5-sou ti7 to2-ui7? Lau7-su li2 ti7 hak8-seng e5 bak8-chiu-cheng5, Ia5-sou na7 si7 ho2, li2 tai7-seng oh8 Ia5-sou, hou7 Ia5-sou kiu3-tioh8--e5 tou be7 ho2 lah, beh kio3 goa2 sin3 li2 sou2 kai3-siau7 e5 Ia5-sou, che chin oh. Gin2-na2 lai5 kau3-hoe7, m7 na7 beh khoaN3 lau7-su, bok8-su, tiuN2-lo2, chip-su7, pe7-bo2, hiaN-che2, lian5 pai3-tng5 it-chhe3 e5 heng5-su7 tou si7 in sou2 beh khoaN3, beh hak8-sip8 e5 tui3-siong7. Li2 kong2 Ia5-sou goa7 ho2, thoan5-kau3-chia2 kap tiong2-chip be7 ho5, hoe7-iu2 tu2 hoe7-iu2 oan-ke, Chu2-jit8-oh8 kau3-sek-lai7 lau7-su kong2 sin3 Ia5-sou si7 goa7 ho2, che long2 pian2--e5, bo5 hau7. 
  3. Choe3-au7 e5 hong-hoat chiu7-si7 ¡§ThiaN3¡¨, ti7-chia sou2 kong2 e5 thiaN3 m7 si7 siok8-tek jin5-cheng5 e5 thiaN3: Eros (E-lou-suh) e5 thiaN3. Si7 kong2 siok8-leng5, seng3-kiat, chu3-seng5 e5 thiaN3: Agape (A-ka-pheh) e5 thiaN3, chit-e5 thiaN3 e5 hoat-goan5 chiu7-si7 Siong7-te3. Iok-han7 it-su kong2 ¡§Siong7-te3 chiu7-si7 thiaN3.¡¨ Siong7-te3 e5 thiaN3 e5 piau2-hian7 chiu7-si7 chai7 ti7 ¡§chhe I e5 kiaN2 ui7-tioh8 lan2 e5 choe7 choe3 ban2-hoe5 e5 che3.¡¨ (I Iok-han7 4:10). Sou2-i2 choe3 lau7-su e5 eng-kai tioh8 u7 Hui-lip8-pi2 2 chiuN sou2 kong2 e5 cheng-sin5, eng7 Chu2 e5 sim choe3 sim, chiu7-si7 ¡§Hoan2-tng2 piaN3-khang ka-ki7, chhu2 lou5-pok8 e5 heng5-chong7, chiaN5 choe3 lang5 e5 iuN7-siuN3, i2-keng u7 chhin-chhiuN7 lang5 e5 khoan2-sit, sun7-hok8 kau3 ti7 si2, sim7-chi3 si2 ti7 sip8-ke3.¡¨ Che chiu7-si7 thiaN3 e5 kek8-ti3, seng-hoa, koh-khah ho2 bo5 lah, che chiu7-si7 bu5-siong7 e5 thiaN3. 
  To7-siong7 kau3-iok8-hoat goa2 siuN7 chiu7-si7 an2-ni: (1) Li2, choe3 lau7-su tioh8 ka-ki7 tai7-seng pa2-ak, tit-tioh8 Ia5-sou. (2) Li2 e7 tit ho2-taN2 kio3 hak8-seng, pi7 kau3-iok8-chia2 oh8 li2, chhin-chhiuN7 li2 u7 oh8 Ki-tok. (3) Chiu7-si7 tioh8 the2-thiap Chu2 e5 sim, kam-goan7 chiong li2 e5 si5-kan, cheng-sin5, ti3-sek, seng-khu, siN3-mia7, thou2 oe7 kong2 ¡§ham7-sin kap mia7¡¨ long2-chong2 hian3 hou7 Chu2 lai5 ui7-tioh8 hak8-seng. Eng7 chit khoan2 e5 thai3-tou7 lai5 leng2-to7 hak8-seng, in-ui7 goa2 chhim-sin3 beh chhoa7 lang5 kau3 ti7 Chu2, che m7 si7 thau5-khak, heng5-ji5-ha7 e5 kau3-iok8, si7 siok8 ti7 sim-leng5, heng5-ji5-siong7 e5 kau3-iok8, si7 i2 sim hoe7 sim, i2 sin5 hoe7 sin5, jin5-keh-tek kau-liu5 e5 kau3-iok8, si7 tioh8 u7 Chu2 e5 Sin5, Seng3 Leng5 e5 khe2-si7, pang-chan7 chiah e7 thang seng5-kong e5 kau3-iok8. Sou2-i2 na7 m7 si7 pun2-sin u7 chin-chiaN3 tit-tioh8 tui3 teng2-bin7 lai5 e5 lek8-liong7 kap thiaN3-sim ia7 eng7 an2-ni lai5 choe3 chiah-e5 kang, tu5 an2-ni i2-goa7 chiu7 i sou2 choe3 e5 it-chhe3 si7 hong7-heng5 kou3-su7 e5 hu-ian2 na7-tiaN7. Po2-lo5 tui3 Ko-lim5-to lang5 kong2, ¡§Ti7 Ki-tok Ia5-sou, goa2 bat tui3 hok-im lai5 siN lin2, sou2-i2 goa2 khng3 lin2 tioh8 oh8 goa2.¡¨ (I Lim5 4:16). Eng7 chit khoan2 e5 sim-cheng5, kap lo5-khou2 lai5 seN sin3-giong2 e5 kiaN2, chit khoan2 lau7-su chiah e7 seng5-kong. 
  Sou2-i2 lau7-su, lan2 tioh8 ka-ki7 tai7-seng chiaN5 choe3 ki5-to2 e5 lang5, m7 na7 si7 choe3 thak8 Seng3-keng sek8-sek8 e5 lang5, kok-khah iau3-kin2 tioh8 chiaN5 choe3 sit8-heng5 Seng3-keng e5 lang5, kan2-tit8 lai5 kong2, lan2 tioh8 choe3 Ia5-sou e5 cheng3-jin5, tui3 Ia5-sou lai5 tit-kiu3, chiaN5-seng3 e5 ¡§Sin5-jin5¡¨, lai5 khia7 ti7 hak8-seng e5 bin7-cheng5. Hou7 hak8-seng tui3 li2 e5 bin7, kap heng5-ui5 lai5 khoaN3-kiN3 Chu2 e5 eng5-kng, an2-ni chiah u7 lat8. An2-ni li2 ku3-ku3 e5 oe7 chiah e7 khap8-tioh8 hak8-seng e5 sim-hian5, thou2-oe7 kong2 ¡§Sim-koaN iN2-a2¡¨, lau5 chhim-khek e5 in3-siong7 ti7 hak8-seng e5 sim-leng5 siong7. Na7 kan-ta hi-hi hoa7-hoa7, kong2 kou3-su7, chhio3-chhio3 leh, liam7 b. ch. chh koa, bok8-koai3 hak8-seng kam2-kak ta-so3 bo5 bi7, kau3 chhou-tiong e5 ni5-leng5, chiu7 khoaN3-khin Chu2-jit8-oh8, choe3 i khi3 bo5 oat8-thau5 lah. 
